import {Component, OnInit} from '@angular/core';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-create-user',
  templateUrl: './create-user.component.html',
  styleUrls: ['./create-user.component.css']
})
export class CreateUserComponent implements OnInit {
  constructor() {
  }

  ngOnInit() {
  }

  submit() {

  }
}
<form method="post" action="http://localhost:8080/register"> <!--(ngSubmit)="submit()"-->>
  <app-text-field-placeholder
    placeholder="Email"
    [required]="true"
  ></app-text-field-placeholder>

  <app-text-field
    fieldName="Пароль"
    [required]="true"
    [nextLine]="false"
  ></app-text-field>

  <app-text-field
    fieldName="Подтверждение пароля"
    [required]="true"
    [nextLine]="false"
  ></app-text-field>

  <app-text-field
    fieldName="Имя" [required]="true"
    [nextLine]="false"
  ></app-text-field>

  <app-text-field
    fieldName="Фамилия"
    [required]="true"
    [nextLine]="false"
  ></app-text-field>

  <app-text-field
    fieldName="Номер телефона"
    [required]="false"
    [nextLine]="false"
  ></app-text-field>

  <button
    type="submit"
    class="py-2 px-4 mt-3 mx-auto rounded-1 bg-blue-600 text-white"
  >Создать</button>
</form>
